46:02.960 --> 46:09.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Whether the old-fashioned
politicians or the
friends of the press like it or
not, it will

46:09.634 --> 46:11.235 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
