46:11.268 --> 46:16.807 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The genie will not go back into
the bottle
again, whether you like it or
not.

46:16.841 --> 46:22.279 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Of all the
nationalist grouping
here, it is the Alternative for
Germany Party

46:22.313 --> 46:27.818 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
which appears to be faltering,
although it
remains the third most popular
in the country.

46:27.852 --> 46:32.690 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
